nodes.bodyText:
Using Pair is a code smell. The above isn't the interface in the related ticket:
public interface SignatureFileReader {
  FileStreamSignature read(InputStream inputStream);
}

I was actually thinking the SignatureFileReader.read() would be moved earlier to Downloader.downloadSigFiles().
    InputStream inputStream = FileUtils.openQuietly(pendingDownload.getFile());
    FileStreamSignature fileStreamSignature = signatureFileReader.read(inputStream);
    fileStreamSignature.setFile(sigFile);
    fileStreamSignature.setNodeAccountId(nodeAccountId);
    sigFilesMap.put(sigFile.getName(), fileStreamSignature);
I think sig files are pretty lightweight we can do this earlier even before reaching 1/3.

